{
  "stem": "25598.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And besides, I didn't know if Tosia will still like me if I don't have that gorgeous, long hair.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I wanted him to like me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I mean, that was one bright spot for me in Shargorod.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So my hair was cut.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then there weren't any things to barter anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So the peasants used to come and bring wool, but that wool was not like we know wool today.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "It was very rough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they used to bring some kind of wires for knitting the wool.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And all the women were knitting sweaters, or scarves, or socks, or gloves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And the men were taken out to labor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And after knitting only for 5 or 10 minutes, because the wool was so rough, and these wires were so rough, everybody's hands were bleeding.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And the skin was coming off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And those sweaters, they-- they all were red or reddish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And that that was not their color.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They were red from blood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But it was one way of getting a bag of potatoes, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] For somehow, babushka managed to get vodka from somebody who brought it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And she had-- there was one piece of furniture in the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "It was a broken stool, and then there was this big sort of shelf structure.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And she put the vodka on the very top shelf.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "I-- I cannot to this day understand how she got to it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "But she did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "But one day, Tosia went after-- no, no, the little one, Musia went after this bottle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And-- and there was a big scandal, because he-- he had been stealing from the vodka.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And he put it back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Like he took a few swigs and put it back.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
